  <data key="d0">"CATEGORY"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The accumulating debt of the welfare state, described as following a 'fatal progression equation' over 50 years."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-de1e838c4a16c8ea8dfe127a589137ac</data>
</node>
