  <data key="d1">"A figure cited in the discussion who made a diagnosis that France is undergoing a 'third-worldization'."&lt;SEP&gt;"Nicolas Bavray is a name used to refer to Nicolas Dufourcq by Philippe Aghion, indicating a possible nickname or mispronunciation."</data>
