  <data key="d1">"Raymond Barr was a European commissioner who advised General de Gaulle against currency devaluation in 1969."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-de1e838c4a16c8ea8dfe127a589137ac</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;SERVICES PUBLICS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CATEGORY"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Public services are mentioned as a national priority that requires refinancing, with savings from pension reform seen as a potential source of funds."</data>
