</node>
<node id="&quot;CHANTIER NAVAL&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The shipyard is the French company where the Swedish manager worked and implemented a consultative restructuring process, contrasting with typical French management styles."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-4d1c98cbcc5c65952fc4e69108ecc5d8</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;ALLEMAGNE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Germany (Allemagne) is cited as a counter-example to France, specifically for having more employee presence on corporate boards and a culture of discussion and respect in the workplace."&lt;SEP&gt;"Germany is mentioned as a comparative example for healthcare systems with co-payment models."&lt;SEP&gt;"Germany is mentioned as the location where Raymond Aron spent a year and where a significant anecdote about political responsibility took place."&lt;SEP&gt;"Germany, cited as a European country with a strong welfare system where 'deaths of despair' have not increased."&lt;SEP&gt;"Germany, mentioned as being ready to invest in France, indicating an important economic and political partnership."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-4d1c98cbcc5c65952fc4e69108ecc5d8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f44f51fafa9fb2ab36dcce22ab1fd71d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-61659a768934b7ee8b99c4caa2dc73f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c40155ff1959faacc40ac81a1bd82732&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c0fa7905a87ac3fcff901f5c962535c9</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;ÉTATS-UNIS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The United States, used as a comparative example of a country with a weaker social safety net and higher healthcare costs."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-f44f51fafa9fb2ab36dcce22ab1fd71d</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;ODILE JACOB&quot;">
