  <data key="d2">chunk-118614beec01eb5355b255debcebf23c</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;SUÉDOIS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"A Swedish manager who ran a shipyard in France. He is presented as a positive example of consultative management, as he involved his employees in a restructuring plan, which they noted was a first for them."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-4d1c98cbcc5c65952fc4e69108ecc5d8</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;ITALIE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Italy, mentioned as a counterexample to France, with a reference to its political leader Meloni, to contrast France's role in Europe."</data>
