</node>
<node id="&quot;TOCQUEVILLE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"A historical French political thinker referenced for his concept of 'democratic individualism' and its societal implications."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-f44f51fafa9fb2ab36dcce22ab1fd71d</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;GABRIEL ZUCMAN&quot;">
