<node id="&quot;FRANCE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
  <data key="d1">"A country described as a welfare state with strong social protections, including free healthcare and education, and stable inequality levels."&lt;SEP&gt;"France is a country facing demographic challenges including declining birth rates and an aging population, with discussions about social security reform."&lt;SEP&gt;"France is a nation-state discussed as having a historical vocation, being a pillar of Europe, and facing challenges with its social model and republican promises."&lt;SEP&gt;"France is the country being discussed, particularly regarding its pension reforms, social policies, and economic history."&lt;SEP&gt;"France is the country whose social system, debt, and economic policies are the central topic of the discussion."&lt;SEP&gt;"France is the nation whose pension system, political climate, and citizenry are the central subject of the entire discussion."&lt;SEP&gt;"France is the national context for the entire discussion. The debate centers on its economic policies, national debt, technological competitiveness, and social model."&lt;SEP&gt;"France is the primary geographic location of the discussion. The text explores the 'spécificité française' (French specificity) regarding its work culture, pension system, and social model."&lt;SEP&gt;"The country being discussed in terms of economic policies, tax measures, and AI development competitiveness."&lt;SEP&gt;"The country being discussed, with its economic policies and welfare state as the central topic of the debate."&lt;SEP&gt;"The country being discussed, with its economic policies, public services, and fiscal challenges as the central topic."&lt;SEP&gt;"The nation-state being discussed, described as a great country, the pillar of Europe, and facing challenges with its social model and debt."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-14e4b66af7e240a6e454da971c593ede&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4d1c98cbcc5c65952fc4e69108ecc5d8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5a6c18fd60d725c0dd2b48e489b44a89&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c0fa7905a87ac3fcff901f5c962535c9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b901d171dd5785e4ce0ac05b882d406d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5fb2a574f750d88794cd45cf0819ffea&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2f7aa0930a810d99a7277de4db2ec96f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f44f51fafa9fb2ab36dcce22ab1fd71d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-61659a768934b7ee8b99c4caa2dc73f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c40155ff1959faacc40ac81a1bd82732&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bc173c20fe16236b49dc39f9e7d15fcf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-de1e838c4a16c8ea8dfe127a589137ac</data>
