  <data key="d3">18.0</data>
  <data key="d4">"Nicolas Dufourcq identifies pension reform as a key solution to free up resources for other underfunded public services."&lt;SEP&gt;"Nicolas Dufourcq provides a detailed philosophical and economic explanation for the necessity of the pension reform, including raising the retirement age."</data>
