  <data key="d3">8.0</data>
  <data key="d4">"Nicolas Dufourcq discusses the points-based system as a desirable but complex reform that creates a 'veil of ignorance' allowing for parameter adjustments."</data>
  <data key="d5">"policy discussion, complexity"</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-5a6c18fd60d725c0dd2b48e489b44a89</data>
